== 操作系统 ==

从[[地球模拟器|地球模拟器]]超算之后，十多年来所有最快的超级计算机都使用基于[[Linux|Linux]]的操作系统。自2017年11月起，所有列出的超级计算机都使用基于[[Linux内核|Linux内核]]的操作系统。<ref name="top500stats">{{cite web | title=Top500 – List Statistics | trans-title=Top500 – 列表统计 | date=2017-11 | url=https://www.top500.org/statistics/details/osfam/1 | website=www.top500.org | language=en | accessdate=2019-03-04 | archive-date=2012-11-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121119205719/https://www.top500.org/statistics/details/osfam/1 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title=Linux Runs All of the World’s Fastest Supercomputers | trans-title=全球所有最快超算均运行于Linux | url=https://www.linuxfoundation.org/blog/linux-runs-all-of-the-worlds-fastest-supercomputers/ | publisher=[[Linux基金会|Linux基金会]] | accessdate=2017-11-30 | language=en | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201031412/https://www.linuxfoundation.org/blog/linux-runs-all-of-the-worlds-fastest-supercomputers/ | archive-date=2017-12-01 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>

自2015年11月以来，列表中就没有计算机运行Windows了。2014年11月，[[Windows_Azure|Windows Azure]]<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.top500.org/site/50454 | title=Microsoft Windows Azure | trans-title=微软Windows Azure | language=en | accessdate=2019-03-04 | archive-date=2019-02-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190221112124/https://www.top500.org/site/50454 | dead-url=no }}</ref>云计算机就退出最快超算列表了（其最佳排名为2012年的第165位）。此时，列表中基于Windows的超算就只剩下[[上海超级计算中心|上海超级计算中心]]的“魔方”（Magic Cube）一台了，它最后一次出现在列表中是在2015年6月发布的名单中排名436，而其最佳排名为2008年的第11位。<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.top500.org/system/176118 | title=Magic Cube – Dawning 5000A, QC Opteron 1.9GHz, Infiniband, Windows HPC 2008 | trans-title=魔方 – 曙光5000A，QC Opteron 1.9GHz，InfiniBand，Windows HPC 2008 | language=en | accessdate=2019-03-04 | archive-date=2019-02-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190221112108/https://www.top500.org/system/176118 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

[[MIPS架构|MIPS]]系统退出榜单已经十多年了，<ref>{{Cite web | url=https://www.top500.org/system/167525 | title=ORIGIN 2000 195/250 MHz {{!}} TOP500 Supercomputer Sites | trans-title=ORIGIN 2000 195/250 MHz {{!}} TOP500超级计算机网站 | website=www.top500.org | language=en | accessdate=2017-11-15 | archive-date=2017-11-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171116025633/https://www.top500.org/system/167525 | dead-url=no }}</ref>但2017年11月（经过大幅升级后）跃升至第四位的{{link-en|晓光 (超级计算机)|Gyoukou|晓光}}超算使用了MIPS作为协处理器一小部分。该超算使用了2,048核协处理器（而每个协处理器又有8×6核MIPS，使其“不再依赖外部的英特尔至强E5主机处理器”<ref>{{Cite news | url=https://en.wikichip.org/wiki/pezy/pezy-scx/pezy-sc2 | title=PEZY-SC2 - PEZY | accessdate=2017-11-17 | language=en | archive-date=2017-11-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171114205300/https://en.wikichip.org/wiki/pezy/pezy-scx/pezy-sc2 | dead-url=no }}</ref>），这使其比超算前10名中的其它超算更加节能。它在[[Green500|Green500]]上排名第五，而基于ZettaScaler-2.2的系统则占据了前三位。<ref>{{Cite news | url=https://fuse.wikichip.org/news/191/the-2048-core-pezy-sc2-sets-a-green500-record/ | title=The 2,048-core PEZY-SC2 sets a Green500 record | trans-title=2,048核的PEZY-SC2写进Green500记录 | date=2017-11-01 | work=WikiChip Fuse | accessdate=2017-11-15 | language=en | quote=Powering the ZettaScaler-2.2 is the PEZY-SC2. The SC2 is a second-generation chip featuring twice as many cores{{snd}} i.e., 2,048 cores with 8-way SMT for a total of 16,384 threads. [..] The first-generation SC incorporated two ARM926 cores and while that was sufficient for basic management and debugging its processing power was inadequate for much more. The SC2 uses a hexa-core P-Class P6600 MIPS processor which share the same memory address as the PEZY cores, improving performance and reducing data transfer overhead. With the powerful MIPS management cores, it is now also possible to entirely eliminate the Xeon host processor. However, PEZY has not done so yet. [驱动ZettaScaler-2.2的是PEZY-SC2。SC2是第二代芯片，其核心数也达到了两倍。也就是说，2,048核带8向SMT，总共就会有16,384个线程。……第一代SC合并了两个ARM926核心，当其基础管理和调试足够用时，其处理能力便捉襟见肘。SC2使用一个六核P级P6600 MIPS处理器（它与PEZY核共享同样的内存地址），来提高性能并降低数据传输消耗。有了强大的MIPS管理核，它现在还可以完全取代至强主机处理器。然而，PEZY并没有这样做。] | archive-date=2017-11-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171116033345/https://fuse.wikichip.org/news/191/the-2048-core-pezy-sc2-sets-a-green500-record/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>它是迄今为止最大的系统，达到了1986万个核心，这几乎是TOP500中最[[多核处理器|多核]]系统（中国的[[神威·太湖之光|神威·太湖之光]]，目前排名第四）的两倍。

